===============================================================================
            Plugin for connect CopterControl board to simulator.
===============================================================================

---------------------------------------
        Building
---------------------------------------

a) download and install:
    - MinGW 4.4
    - Qt 4.8
b) run:
    qmake
    mingw32-make

---------------------------------------
        Installing
---------------------------------------

1a) Copy folder "CopterControl" from build location to simulator's "Plugin" folder.
1b) Copy QtCore4.dll, QtNetwork4.dll, libgcc_s_dw2-1.dll and mingwm10.dll from
    Qt library location to the root folder of simulator.
  or
2) Uncomment 4-th line in copydata.pri and set the variable SIM_DIR to point 
   to the root of the simulator. Then after compiling all the libraries and plug-in
   will be copied automatically

---------------------------------------
        Configure plugin
---------------------------------------

See cc_plugin.ini
You can change network settings, input and output channels map, video modes.

---------------------------------------
        Tools
---------------------------------------

"tools\udp_test" utility can be used for test connection.
